---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | Zeke Abshire" description="">
    <h1 class="my-6 mt-14 text-4xl font-semibold">About Me</h1>
    <p class="my-3 text-lg leading-loose text-mix">
        Howdy, I'm Zeke, and I'm a software developer with well over 6 years of
        experience.
        <br />
        I have a strong background in full-stack web development, mobile app development,
        and data science. I've worked on a variety of projects ranging from programming
        language interpreters to MVP websites and apps for startups.
    </p>

    <h2 class="my-4 mt-10 text-3xl font-semibold" id="skills">Skills</h2>
    <div
        class="my-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-y-6 gap-x-6 text-lg text-mix xs:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4"
    >
        <div>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-fg">Languages</h3>
            <ul class="ml-5 list-outside list-disc">
                <li>TypeScript</li>
                <li>JavaScript</li>
                <li>Python</li>
                <li>Dart</li>
                <li>C#</li>
                <li>Java</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-fg">Frameworks</h3>
            <ul class="ml-5 list-outside list-disc">
                <li>React.js</li>
                <li>Next.js</li>
                <li>Astro.js</li>
                <li>React Native</li>
                <li>Flutter</li>
                <li>TailwindCSS</li>
                <li>SCSS</li>
                <li>MUI</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-fg">Tools</h3>
            <ul class="ml-5 list-outside list-disc">
                <li>Figma</li>
                <li>Blender</li>
                <li>Inkscape</li>
                <li>Gimp</li>
                <li>Google Analytics</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold text-fg">Experience</h3>
            <ul class="ml-5 list-outside list-disc">
                <li>Team Leadership</li>
                <li>Accessibility</li>
                <li>SEO</li>
                <li>Software Architecture</li>
                <li>Data Science</li>
                <li>Agile/Scrum</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="my-4 mt-10 text-3xl font-semibold" id="certifications">
        Certifications
    </h2>
    <ul class="my-3 ml-5 list-outside list-disc text-lg text-mix">
        <li>DELF B2 French proficiency</li>
        <li>Secret-level clearance</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="my-4 mt-10 text-3xl font-semibold" id="education">Education</h2>
    <p class="my-3 text-lg leading-loose text-mix">
        I earned two bachelor's degrees from Louisiana State University: one in
        Computer Science and one in Math. I graduated in May 2023 with a
        cumulative GPA of 4.05.
    </p>

    <h2 class="my-4 mt-10 text-3xl font-semibold" id="awards">Awards</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-row">
        <ul
            class="my-5 ml-[40%] border-l-2 border-fg pl-6 text-lg text-mix xs:ml-[30%] md:ml-[20%] lg:ml-[15%]"
        >
            <li data-semester="Spring 2023" class="award-element my-5">
                B.S. in Computer Science and B.S. in Mathematics
            </li>
            <li data-semester="Fall 2022" class="award-element my-5">
                Dean's List
            </li>
            <li data-semester="Summer 2022" class="award-element my-5">
                Secret-level clearance
            </li>
            <li data-semester="Spring 2022" class="award-element my-5">
                Peg and Tom Madden Mathematics Research Scholarship, President's
                Honor Roll
            </li>
            <li data-semester="Fall 2021" class="award-element my-5">
                President's Honor Roll
            </li>
            <li data-semester="Spring 2021" class="award-element my-5">
                President's Honor Roll
            </li>
            <li data-semester="Fall 2020" class="award-element my-5">
                Dean's List
            </li>
            <li>...</li>
            <li data-semester="Spring 2019" class="award-element my-5">
                DELF B2 Certification
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <h2 class="my-4 mt-10 text-3xl font-semibold" id="hobbies">Hobbies</h2>
    <p class="my-3 text-lg leading-loose text-mix">
        I am passionate about using technology to solve problems and make a
        positive impact, and I am always looking for new challenges and
        opportunities to learn and grow. In my free time, I play musical
        instruments and learn new languages. I've been playing stringed
        instruments for about 7 years now, and I've been learning French since
        kindergarten and many other languages recently.
    </p>

    <p class="my-3 text-lg leading-loose text-mix">
        Thank you for visiting my portfolio!
    </p>
</Layout>
